description:
Danny and pop culture writer/podcaster/Twitter sensation/friend Ira Madison III drink prosecco, break down the Oscar nominations, #PumpRules pasta-gate, The View, and so many other things going on in pop culture. Ira also tells us about his new podcast, Keep It!, from Crooked Media. 

Hosted on Acast. See acast.com/privacy for more information.
